title: terminated base (genetics)
pid: 9648d682-4f6f-47f2-bd74-ed84f979d28c
body: |2-
  These are bases modified so that once the DNAP pairs them to a strand,
  no more bases can be added.
  They are also modified so that each of the four kinds (C,G,A,T)
  glows a different color when illuminated.
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
